These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, cain, fonseca
4 different pets are kept: snake, fish, pony, cat
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, puzzles, writing
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, egyptian, indonesian, french
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, funk, r&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, turquise, lilac, grey
 1. the french is on the far right##1
 2. the cain-smoker is the fan of classical##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the indonesian is between the person who likes blue and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the right of the turkish##1
10. the person who likes blue is between the indonesian and the owner of the cat##2
11. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
12. the french is the person who's hobby is writing##1
13. the fan of funk is between the fan of dubstep and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Cigar      | fonseca        | baccarat       | cain  | bongani |
| Pet          | cat     | pony         | fish     | snake    |
| Hobby         | gardening  | fishing      | puzzles   | writing     |
| Nationality           | egyptian | turkish | indonesian   | french     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | funk         | classical | r&b         |
| Color         | grey     | blue     | turquise  | lilac       |

