.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
City: boston, colone, london, liverpool
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, canasta, domino, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
4 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, pony, cat
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, apricot, lilac, yellow
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the person who likes apricot is between the person playing domino and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is between the person traveling to boston and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the owner of the frog is the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person playing scrabble##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the frog is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
13. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| City      | liverpool    | colone       | london   | boston |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | domino   | scrabble    | canasta  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
| Pet   | cat    | frog       | hedgehog | pony        |
| Color   | yellow | lilac   | apricot     | brown    |
| Transport     | bus       | ship        | train      | bike        |

