 9. the person eating apple is between the chaman-smoker and the owner of the bird##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating apple##1
12. the blend-smoker is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the townhouse house is the townhouse house##1
14. the owner of the rabbit is the american##1

