 1. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the engineer is on the far right##1
 3. the person playing domino is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is between the firefighter and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the person eating carrot is the person playing scrabble##1
 6. the firefighter is on the right of the modern house##1
 7. the person playing go is on the far right##1
 8. the palace house is on the left of the tower house##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
10. the person playing domino is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the person eating pepper is on the left of the bartender##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
