.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, parkour, baseball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, animation, disaster, satire
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar, montecristo, dannemann
4 different games are played: canasta, chess, domino, backgammon
There are 4 different nationalities: american, british, dutch, german
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rat, turtle
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the american##1
 2. the dutch is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person watching satire movies##2
 7. the german is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 9. the german is the person watching horror movies##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the rat##1
13. the person playing domino is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport      | baseball        | parkour     | swimming        | basketball    |
| Movie-Genre          | disaster     | animation   | horror   | satire |
| Cigar           | dannemann | pall-mall  | bolivar | montecristo |
| Game   | chess            | domino    | backgammon        | canasta  |
| Nationality   | dutch          | american | german      | british  |
| Pet           | mouse          | frog     | turtle      | rat      |

