.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, september, august, january
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise, grey, lilac
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, blues, classical, gospel
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, satire, thriller
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, tiparillo, old-henry
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in september is the old-henry-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is between the fan of classical and the person who likes lilac##2
 8. the fan of classical is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is between the owner of the mouse and the tiparillo-smoker##2
10. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
11. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
13. the person who likes grey is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | january        | august      | september | february       |
| Color         | grey | chestnut | lilac   | turquise   |
| Music-Genre           | classical | gospel     | blues        | metal   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | thriller    | documentary | satire    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | dunhill      | old-henry      | blend |
| Pet           | ferret      | goldfish    | mouse       | hedgehog  |

