.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, july, november
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, freelancer, pilot, security-guard
City: hannover, edinburgh, venice, rome
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel, satire, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, trike, ship, roller
 1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the chef is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person watching romance movies and the person driving the trike##2
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is the security-guard##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
13. the person traveling to hannover is between the chef and the person driving the motorbike##2
14. the security-guard is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea      | hot-chocolate | lemonade       | mirinda   |
| Birthday          | september   | july          | november           | march |
| Job           | chef     | freelancer    | security-guard | pilot     |
| City   | rome   | hannover          | edinburgh         | venice     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | romance      | horror       | satire    |
| Transport           | roller | ship       | motorbike         | trike  |

