.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, sunflower, begonia, poppy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, cain, siglo, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, may, february
4 different games are played: poker, chess, backgammon, billiard
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, italian, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, train, trike
 1. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person driving the car is on the right of the australian##1
 6. the cain-smoker is between the person driving the car and the british##2
 7. the person driving the trike is between the australian and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
10. the siglo-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the british##1
12. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
13. the italian is the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the cain-smoker is the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |       3       |      4      |
| Flower          | poppy     | begonia        | sunflower         | bellflower   |
| Cigar         | aristoff     | siglo     | cain    | tiparillo |
| Birthday           | september  | february      | may | july   |
| Game   | chess   | billiard | backgammon        | poker       |
| Nationality   | turkish    | british     | australian    | italian     |
| Transport     | snowmobile | trike       | train         | car         |

