.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, punk, indie
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, mauve, yellow, amber
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, puzzles, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, azalea, poppy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, soccer, cricket, sailing
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, russian, thai
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 3. the mexican is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the russian##1
10. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan of indie and the person who growsazalea##2
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop | punk         | indie       | soul         |
| Color          | aquamarine | mauve  | yellow        | amber         |
| Hobby         | puzzles | photography | cooking     | woodworking   |
| Flower           | azalea | orchid  | marigold | poppy |
| Sport   | cricket  | sailing     | soccer       | golf   |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani   | thai        | mexican       |

