.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, eggplant, pepper, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, july, february, april
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, electrician, fisherman, coach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, house, metal, blues
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, white, green, red
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
 3. the lawyer is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the coach is the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes ivory##1
 8. the person who likes white is the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the electrician is the person who likes red##1
10. the coach is on the right of the fisherman##1
11. the fan of blues is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's birthday is in august##2
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite     | mirinda  | iced-tea |
| Food          | artichoke     | pepper     | eggplant | pumpkin  |
| Birthday         | april   | august | july  | february   |
| Job   | electrician         | fisherman   | coach   | lawyer |
| Music-Genre         | house       | metal    | blues   | rock |
| Color     | red        | ivory   | green   | white      |

 